Abstract = {With the rapid development of artificial intelligence technology, the
   era of AIGC is coming. This paper relies on the Metaverse theoretical
   system to conduct analysis and research from the perspective of AIGC
   core technology as well as AIGC application cases. Take ChatGPT and
   ERNIE Bot as products examples. Besides, security challenges are taken
   into consideration, it brings the risk of sensitive content, it leads to
   lower costs for criminal activities, it brings cross-border data
   security risk, and it will even reduce the public's thinking ability. To
