   Univ; Hubei Univ Technol; IEEE},
Abstract = {Expert knowledge in the criminal investigation area is mostly empirical
   and tacit, which brings great difficulties to construct criminal
   investigation decision support system (CIDSS). Case-based reasoning
   (CBR) is a kind of incremental learning method that records
   successful-solved cases with their experiences to effectively overcome
   the bottleneck of knowledge acquisition and be helpful to solve similar
   crime problems. From the actual demands of police force, author designs
   a framework of CIDSS based on case reasoning, and discusses its
   function, process, and technical points, so as to provide a feasible
   tool for criminal investigation, crisis intervention and early warning.},
